}}

Oswald is the assistant of the illustrious [[Durin]]! He must prevent people from bothering Durin and is rather vague in his explanations. Could this Durin be the great [[god]] of the [[dwarf|dwarves]]?<br>
Oswald spreads false rumours, and is somewhat disliked by the other citizens of Thais.<br />
