Alesar is somewhat special because he is a [[Blue Djinn]] who switched sides and is working for the green djinns in [[Mal'ouquah]] now. He does not like humans, but will tolerate those who help fight for [[Malor]] and the [[Green Djinn]].<br /> He and [[Yaman]] deal in strong weapons and armor for the [[Efreet]] and [[Green Djinn]] army.
He is a brother of [[Haroun]].
