Al Dee supplies the city with [[equipment]]. He is a hotshot guy who wants to be the only merchant on [[Rookgaard]] and is therefore called Mad Al. He is an [[Allusions#Aldi|allusion]] to German supermarket [[wikipedia:Aldi|Aldi]]. His brother [[Gree Dee]], who works in Yalahar, is an [[Equipment Shopkeeper NPCs|Equipment Shopkeeper]] as well. He may be related to [[Barnabas Dee]], sorcerer from Rathleton.<br />[[Sign]]s advertising Al Dee's wares can be found in many strange and obscure places, including the following:<br />
In the [[Al Dee Rat Cave|Rat cave nearest to him]] there is a sign that says:
:{{Message|type=look|You read: Buy ropes at Al Dee's shop.}}
There is another one near the bridge crossing to the western wilderness area:
:{{Message|type=look|You read: Never enter dungeons without a rope or you may be lost forever.<br />Al Dee's shop - come to where the ropes are!}}
Deep in the dungeons of [[Rookgaard]] there is a sign that tells:
:{{Message|type=look|Feeling alone in the dark?<br />Is your torch running out?<br />Al Dee's shop - come to where the torches are!}}
Another sign deep in a cave says:
:{{Message|type=look|You read: Feeling lost?<br />Would you give all your gold for a rope now?<br />Al Dee's shop - come to where the ropes are!}}
Next to Al Dee, there's a [[blackboard]] on which is written the following:
:{{Message|type=look|You read: GENERAL EQUIPMENT:<br />rope, torch,<br />bag, backpack,<br />scroll, sickle,<br />shovel, pick, scythe,<br />fishing rod}}
{{JSpoiler|Talk to him to start the [[Pick Quest]].}}

